29
00:01:09,860 --> 00:01:12,250
because he’s on a strict seafood diet:

30
00:01:12,250 --> 00:01:15,610
When he sees food, he eats it.

31
00:01:15,610 --> 00:01:17,560
The sanctions also prohibit expanding

32
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:20,250
