58
00:02:22,540 --> 00:02:24,890
The US gets cooperation from China on North
Korea

59
00:02:24,890 --> 00:02:26,870
without starting a trade war.

60
00:02:26,870 --> 00:02:27,870
And even though China will take

61
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:30,170
the brunt of the loss in terms of trade,

62
00:02:30,170 --> 00:02:32,120
it’s great PR.

63
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,400
It makes it seem like China

64
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,870
is part of the solution,

65
00:02:34,870 --> 00:02:36,430
not part of the problem.

66
00:02:36,430 --> 00:02:39,090
It also prevents the US from putting more
sanctions

67
00:02:39,090 --> 00:02:41,430
on Chinese companies with dubious ties

68
00:02:41,430 --> 00:02:42,780
to North Korea.

69
00:02:42,780 --> 00:02:44,319
For now at least.

70
00:02:44,319 --> 00:02:48,730
North Korea for its part has not taken the
sanctions well.

71
