89
00:03:48,740 --> 00:03:52,040
Yes, we wouldn’t want anything unbeneficial
happening.

90
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:53,269
But there’s a problem here.

91
00:03:53,269 --> 00:03:55,150
I mean, besides the rogue regime

92
00:03:55,150 --> 00:03:57,069
